snippet: Occupy New Hampshire is seeing Tuesday's primary as a chance to raise their profile -- but many members of the group are distancing themselves from the tactics that saw members of Occupy the Caucus arrested last week in Iowa.
abstract: Occupy New Hampshire is seeing Tuesday's primary as a chance to raise their profile -- but many members of the group are distancing themselves from the tactics that saw members of Occupy the Caucus arrested last week in Iowa.
lead_paragraph: Occupy New Hampshire has a full slate of events ahead of the state's primary on Tuesday, but many members of the group are distancing themselves from some of the tactics that saw members of Occupy the Caucus arrested last week in Iowa.

headline.main: 'Occupy' Protesters in New Hampshire Seek Visibility Ahead of Primary
